cs.CV, cs.OH, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the design of diffractive optical neural networks for optical machine learning tasks, specifically object recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). Other likely categories include optics (cs.OH), information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
